# Retail Sales Data Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes retail sales data using Python.

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Matplotlib

## Features

* Data loading
* Data analysis
* Visualization
* Sales insights

## Project Output

* Sales category analysis
* Bar chart visualization
* Total sales calculation

## Conclusion

This project helps understand customer purchasing behavior and business sales trends.

